面。咁嘅質素點值得我地去尊重佢呀？"},{"pid":"fb527cefb250dea84e1aed680ca514441c2c9274","tid":945781,"uid":170249,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:21:15.000Z","msg":"佢地都唔尊重香港人條命<br />\n<br />\n你講咩尊重？<br />\n<br />\n垃圾777"},{"pid":"c922e1a0496eab1119e053051826f55dddb53998","tid":945781,"uid":90,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:23:40.000Z","msg":"基本上香港人無喇喇畀人殺都好<br />\n只要唔係新移民<br />\n政府都唔會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3f26c280adfc9748b993080198d27b383ff7c1","tid":945781,"uid":90,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:26:33.000Z","msg":"港護照係去得嘅國家多啲<br />\n實質同支那護照一樣垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那護照仲可能有口交部講下<br />\n特區賤民護照求助就踢你去支那領事<br />\n支那領事踢返你去香港度"},{"pid":"0bb73167b368b5f7376c6e4f0e5708ff9df05487","tid":945781,"uid":28155,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:27:49.000Z","msg":"依d 場合<br />\n當奴真係最正常個個"},{"pid":"e7f0f8dd9c82ae26b13449a464a501cecfe33046","tid":945781,"uid":3241,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"請支国尊重加拿大司法制度<br />\n不過渣得支国特蠢護照....都遇左係賤民階級<br />\n利申: 全家英藉"},{"pid":"6dbc66c24488cfd659a2b79293c46260eb61d019","tid":945781,"uid":76705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:34:31.000Z","msg":"建議大家從今日起係所有場合只用港共殖民政府稱呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96971d283a45b0c9ace75d5127809cebba3fb843","tid":945781,"uid":78515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:37:29.000Z","msg":"尊重菲傭來港權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印傭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb968b50ed2f065819672338beeaf67a2aaa6d1","tid":945781,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm